"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"【基础】\\n\\n项目只有统一的代币，游戏内和游戏外的经济循环靠单币维持，例如：Crypto Zoon、\\n\\nPlayvalkyr、Radio Caca等都是采用这种代币模型。\\n\\n![基础流程](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/OjGeB9ht8P1BLKKnRwrTX.png?height=408&width=717)\\n\\n理想状态分析：\\n\\n假设项目初始设计回本周期为20天，代币A的价格Pa=1USD，NFT=500枚A，日产25枚。设初始进场人数Y0，之后日进场人数Y1,Y2,Y3…  要Pa维持不变，则需要日产=日消耗。25Y0=500Y1 , 25(Y0+Y1)=500Y2 , 25(Y0+Y1+Y2)=500Y3…则\",\"timestamp\":1639820546,\"title\":\"GameFi<单币经济模型>\"},\"digest\":\"rRCztbcNQPMMNcDbLaVdydq3hyjUscvVEHdIWJPtUYA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8210A401239F580280Ebf85082278E2266af8B2D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"JgoZ2Q2nqPsy0z8ooNgmKnALs0k35-NRrVqfhwx5gWw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0hnlyauKiu3q_L-vsOge7KID2Ox3TX2tzovj0Rw8TDA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MzWnSdL11O6UqVKTL1udTbEmfaOniKIHhQOQCn24ahC-rvKeXsVMZK34dF4ZM1MowDZd1E4yNCffER13dtyNqw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x008ad5771efcb0f23ebf7d5c7fb4b671eec1ae517b67a30b7808413bb8f6a893492bc01eba204380c4f9553fe190613be166ffed550a291e5834b4ce0ae98a201b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"JgoZ2Q2nqPsy0z8ooNgmKnALs0k35-NRrVqfhwx5gWw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0hnlyauKiu3q_L-vsOge7KID2Ox3TX2tzovj0Rw8TDA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"kDtSm2fL04K2AxZdKhYK_uPlPucz8MwtAkjArZ_aOE8\"}"